            "path": "retro-relevance/SentenceList.tsx",
            "parameters": {
                "key": "test-response1",
                "testingStimulusValue": "# this is markdown.\n It is a long string of text. **General Requirements:**\n\n- **Two Main Study Pages:**\n- **Text Editor (Phase 4):** For participants to edit and author a markdown paragraph.\n- **Paragraph Selection (Phase 5):** For participants to mark regions of a finished paragraph for relevance.\n- Three additional pages:\n\n - **Admin Page:** This page is for study administrators to prepare study data. Administrators can:",
